=Description=

"Village.Builders is a non-profit Think-and-Do Tank, a newly forming distributed volunteer organisation whose purpose is to catalyse the [[Village 3.0 Movement]].
​
We are inspired by the success of rLoop in the Hyperloop Movement, and we hope Village.Builders will do for villages and intentional communities, what rLoop is doing for transportation.
 
Throughout 2017, Village.Builders will be growing its membership and hosting online conversations in the build up to the first Village 3.0 Summit."
(https://www.village.builders/)

